  "updated": 1644910744,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5b73871928c82d00149997f5",
      "text": "対立は一つだけではない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1534297882,
      "updated": 1555467577
    },
    {
      "id": "617266f6aff09e0000cd2960",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/75cdec6c64c18cd269857324144b833d]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1634887414,
      "updated": 1634887415
    },
    {
      "id": "617266f7aff09e0000cd2961",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1634887415,
      "updated": 1634887415
    },
    {
      "id": "620b5661aff09e000064700f",
      "text": "[エンジニアの知的生産術_加筆案]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1644910177,
      "updated": 1644910188
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5a4e5aff09e0000572911",
      "text": "\t[エンジニアの知的生産術] P.161「[(5.2.5.2) NM法は対立関係に着目する]」の最終段落1文目の後で節を区切って、そこに挿入される。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555408102,
      "updated": 1644910190
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb68d23aff09e0000572913",
      "text": "\t[盲点カード]にも入れよう",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555467556,
      "updated": 1644910192
    },
    {
      "id": "617266f2aff09e0000cd295f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1634887411,
      "updated": 1634887411
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb68d23aff09e0000572914",
      "text": "-----",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555467556,
      "updated": 1555467557
    },
    {
      "id": "620b5691aff09e0000647010",
      "text": "[* 対立は一つだけではない]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1644910225,
      "updated": 1644910227
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb68d25aff09e0000572915",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555467557,
      "updated": 1555467557
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb59e4eaff09e00005728e4",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/caab7ed032d988ecce78aec18cb91189]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555406414,
      "updated": 1555406467
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb59e4eaff09e00005728e5",
      "text": " 白と黒の対立",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555406414,
      "updated": 1555406477
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb59e8daff09e00005728ea",
      "text": " すべすべとトゲトゲの対立",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555406477,
      "updated": 1555406477
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb59eb4aff09e00005728ec",
      "text": "どちらも対立である",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555406516,
      "updated": 1555406521
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb59eb9aff09e00005728ed",
      "text": "黒丸も、白トゲトゲも、どちらも白丸と対立している。しかしこの2つは同じものではない。似てもいない。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555406521,
      "updated": 1555406563
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb59ed3aff09e00005728ee",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555406547,
      "updated": 1555406547
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb59f0caff09e00005728f6",
      "text": "ここには白黒とすべすべ/トゲトゲの2つの属性がある。この図に書かれていない「黒トゲトゲ」を加えると、全体ではこういう構造になる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555406605,
      "updated": 1555406636
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb59f2baff09e00005728f7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555406636,
      "updated": 1555406636
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb59f33aff09e00005728f8",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/75cdec6c64c18cd269857324144b833d]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555406644,
      "updated": 1555406644
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb59f34aff09e00005728f9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555406644,
      "updated": 1555406644
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb59efeaff09e00005728ef",
      "text": " 白丸と黒トゲトゲには何も共通点がなくて、[無関係]な情報に見える",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555406591,
      "updated": 1555406597
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb59f05aff09e00005728f0",
      "text": " 「対立している」と感じられるものは、それすら感じられないものに比べると「近い」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555406597,
      "updated": 1644910260
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb59f05aff09e00005728f1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555406597,
      "updated": 1555406687
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb59f05aff09e00005728f4",
      "text": "ここまでの話は、属性が2種類でそれぞれ2通りの値を持つ(白と黒、すべすべとトゲトゲ)世界で話をした。世の中の出来事にはもっとたくさんの属性があり、各属性が多様な値を取りうる。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555406597,
      "updated": 1644910445
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb59f05aff09e00005728f5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555406597,
      "updated": 1555406597
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb59e8daff09e00005728eb",
      "text": "1つの属性には2通りの値しかないシンプルなケースで、属性の数がどのような影響を及ぼすか観察してみよう。図中の線は、1つの属性の値だけが異なる要素をつないでいる。人間が直感的に理解できるのは、3次元の立方体の辺でイメージできる属性が3つの場合が限界だろう。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555406477,
      "updated": 1644910459
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb59f78aff09e00005728fa",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/9fcbc7464466adc85fd566234b410952]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555406712,
      "updated": 1555406712
    },
    {
      "id": "620b57a1aff09e00006f0117",
      "text": " 属性が1つ、2つ、3つ、4つ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1644910497,
      "updated": 1644910497
    },
    {
      "id": "620b57afaff09e00006f0118",
      "text": " 注: 属性4つの図に誤りがある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1644910512,
      "updated": 1644910526
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb59f95aff09e00005728ff",
      "text": "\t脚注: 「ブール束」(boolean lattice)と名前がついている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555406741,
      "updated": 1555406741
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb59f95aff09e0000572900",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555406741,
      "updated": 1555406741
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb59f95aff09e0000572901",
      "text": "対立という言葉で、属性が1つの「善と悪の二項対立」みたいなものをイメージするとよくない。現実は、属性が無数にある。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555406741,
      "updated": 1555406741
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb59f95aff09e0000572902",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555406741,
      "updated": 1555406741
    },
    {
      "id": "620b57f5aff09e0000647011",
      "text": "[(5.2.4.6) 家族的類似性]で紹介した花の絵は、4つの属性を持っている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1644910581,
      "updated": 1644910648
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb59f95aff09e0000572904",
      "text": "\tターゲットの4つの特徴を1111と表現すると、",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555406741,
      "updated": 1555407164
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5a13daff09e0000572906",
      "text": "\tグループ1",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555407165,
      "updated": 1555407168
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5a13faff09e0000572907",
      "text": "\t\t1110, 1010, 1100, 0110",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555407168,
      "updated": 1555407179
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5a14baff09e0000572908",
      "text": "\tグループ2",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555407179,
      "updated": 1555407181
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5a14daff09e0000572909",
      "text": "\t\t0011, 0001, 0101, 1001",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555407182,
      "updated": 1555407193
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5a159aff09e000057290a",
      "text": "\tこれを属性4つのブール束に描いてみると、こうなる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555407194,
      "updated": 1555407292
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb59f91aff09e00005728fb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555406738,
      "updated": 1555406738
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb59f91aff09e00005728fc",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/a6fec999b1f0d3e96be5fbbcb90c8d5d]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555406738,
      "updated": 1555407126
    },
    {
      "id": "620b585daff09e00006f011a",
      "text": "　赤がグループ1、青がグループ2",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1644910685,
      "updated": 1644910707
    },
    {
      "id": "620b5872aff09e00006f011b",
      "text": "　 色で識別するのはあまり良くないので描き直す時に修正する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1644910707,
      "updated": 1644910742
    },
    {
      "id": "620b5896aff09e00006f011c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1644910743,
      "updated": 1644910744
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5a116aff09e00004e3fd5",
      "text": "この図を見るとグループ1の方がグループ2よりもターゲットに近いと感じるだろう。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555407126,
      "updated": 1555407486
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5a27eaff09e000057290b",
      "text": "その感覚は、家族的類似性と違う原因で生まれている。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555407486,
      "updated": 1555407571
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5a2cdaff09e000057290c",
      "text": "グループ1とグループ2の違いは、グループ1には距離1の1110が含まれていて、グループ2は距離3の0001が含まれているところにある。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555407566,
      "updated": 1555407605
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb59f91aff09e00005728fd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555406738,
      "updated": 1555406738
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb59f92aff09e00005728fe",
      "text": "我々は対立について考えるときに、1属性の対立をイメージしてしまいがちだ。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555406738,
      "updated": 1555408043
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5a4b5aff09e000057290f",
      "text": "そして対立しているペアは遠いものであると考えがちだ。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555408054,
      "updated": 1555408065
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5a4aaaff09e000057290d",
      "text": "しかし現実世界には多くの属性がある。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555408043,
      "updated": 1555408053
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5a4b4aff09e000057290e",
      "text": "そしてその状況では、対立しているものは、対立すらしないものに比べて、近い位置にあるのだ。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555408053,
      "updated": 1555408094
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5a4deaff09e0000572910",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555408094,
      "updated": 1555408094
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb59e4eaff09e00005728e6",
      "text": "----",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555406414,
      "updated": 1555406416
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb59e4faff09e00005728e7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555406416,
      "updated": 1555406416
    },
    {
      "id": "5b73870faff09e0000e6362a",
      "text": "from [エンジニアの知的生産術 P150～P168の加筆案]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1534297882,
      "updated": 1534297882
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba3afbaaff09e00007ba1cf",
      "text": "#エンジニアの知的生産術_加筆案",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537454010,
      "updated": 1537454015
    },
    {
      "id": "5b738715aff09e0000e63640",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1534297888,
      "updated": 1534297888
    },
    {
      "id": "5b73870faff09e0000e6362b",
      "text": "\t対立は1種類ではない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1534297882,
      "updated": 1534297888
    },
    {
      "id": "5b73870faff09e0000e6362d",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/caab7ed032d988ecce78aec18cb91189]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1534297882,
      "updated": 1537453823
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba3aefeaff09e0000b76e9a",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/d341de41bc3c1b9bf69ed7490cdae696]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537453823,
      "updated": 1537453823
    },
    {
      "id": "5b73870faff09e0000e6362e",
      "text": " 白と黒の対立",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1534297882,
      "updated": 1534297882
    },
    {
      "id": "5b73870faff09e0000e6362f",
      "text": " すべすべとトゲトゲの対立",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1534297882,
      "updated": 1534297882
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba3af2baff09e0000b76e9b",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/75cdec6c64c18cd269857324144b833d]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537453867,
      "updated": 1537453871
    },
    {
      "id": "5b73870faff09e0000e63630",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1534297882,
      "updated": 1534297882
    },
    {
      "id": "5b73870faff09e0000e63631",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1534297882,
      "updated": 1534297882
    },
    {
      "id": "5b73870faff09e0000e63632",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/708857924cb500bd65900c84f94ca4d8]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1534297882,
      "updated": 1534297882
    },
    {
      "id": "5b73870faff09e0000e63633",
      "text": " 白丸と黒トゲトゲには何も共通点がなくて、[無関係]な情報に見える",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1534297882,
      "updated": 1550491517
    },
    {
      "id": "5b73870faff09e0000e63634",
      "text": " 対立していると感じられるものは、それすら感じられないものに比べると、近い関係",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1534297882,
      "updated": 1534297882
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6a9f8faff09e00004da664",
      "text": " \t[対立は近い関係]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550491535,
      "updated": 1550491541
    },
    {
      "id": "5b73870faff09e0000e63635",
      "text": "\t「[愛の反対は憎しみではなく無関心]」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1534297882,
      "updated": 1550491509
    },
    {
      "id": "5b73870faff09e0000e63636",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1534297882,
      "updated": 1534297882
    },
    {
      "id": "5b73870faff09e0000e63637",
      "text": "ここまででは、属性が2種類(白と黒、すべすべとトゲトゲ)で話をした。世の中の出来事にはもっとたくさんの属性があり、属性が全部でいくつあるのかすら把握できていない。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1534297882,
      "updated": 1534297882
    },
    {
      "id": "5b73870faff09e0000e63638",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1534297882,
      "updated": 1534297882
    },
    {
      "id": "5b73870faff09e0000e63639",
      "text": "1つの属性には2通りの値しかないシンプルなケースで、属性の数がどういう影響を及ぼすか観察してみよう。図中の線は、1つの属性の値だけが異なる要素をつないでいる。人間が直感的に理解できるのは、3次元の立方体の辺でイメージできる属性が3つの場合が限界だろう。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1534297882,
      "updated": 1534297882
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba3af3baff09e0000b76e9d",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/9fcbc7464466adc85fd566234b410952]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537453883,
      "updated": 1537453883
    },
    {
      "id": "5b73870faff09e0000e6363a",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/16b38aa0ee308184ca865d1638475e63]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
